"Adjust the microphone input volume (PipeWire/PulseAudio default source)."
msgstr ""
"Eingangslautstärke des Mikrofons anpassen (PipeWire/PulseAudio "
"Standardquelle)."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:301
msgid "Noise floor:"
msgstr "Grundrauschen:"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:304
msgid "Calibrate"
msgstr "Kalibrieren"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:307
msgid "Recording silence…"
msgstr "Stille aufnehmen…"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:313
msgid ""
"Record 5 seconds of silence to calibrate the background noise level. This "
"improves animation accuracy."
msgstr ""
"5 Sekunden Stille aufnehmen, um den Hintergrundgeräuschpegel zu kalibrieren. "
"Dies verbessert die Animationsgenauigkeit."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:324
msgid "Noise gate:"
msgstr "Noise Gate:"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:338
msgid ""
"Audio levels below this threshold are zeroed. Increase to suppress "
"background noise and get clean silence."
msgstr ""
"Audiopegel unterhalb dieser Schwelle werden auf Null gesetzt. Erhöhen, um "
"Hintergrundgeräusche zu unterdrücken und saubere Stille zu erhalten."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:343
msgid "Envelope shape:"
msgstr "Hüllkurvenform:"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:354
msgid "Flat"
msgstr "Flach"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:356
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Normal"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:362
msgid ""
"Controls the Hanning envelope shape. 0 = flat (uniform bars), 1 = normal, "
"higher = more peaked at the center."
msgstr ""
"Steuert die Hanning-Hüllkurvenform. 0 = flach (gleichmäßige Balken), 1 = "
"normal, höher = stärker zentriert."

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:367
msgid "Envelope center:"
msgstr "Hüllkurvenzentrum:"

#: package/contents/ui/configGeneral.qml:383
msgid ""
"Shift the envelope peak across the frequency range (80–4000 Hz). Useful with "
"rainbow colors to emphasize different frequency bands."
msgstr ""
"Den Hüllkurvenpeak über den Frequenzbereich verschieben (80–4000 Hz). "
"Nützlich mit Regenbogenfarben, um verschiedene Frequenzbänder hervorzuheben."

